      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomato has softened, add the <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong>,<strong> spicy stock</strong>, and <strong>quinoa</strong> to the pan and cook for 15-20 min or until the sweet potato is tender</p>",
