      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Peruvian-style haddock</strong> <strong>&</strong> <strong>sweet potato stew</strong> and garnish with the <strong>reserved coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
